snippet.title: Amber Heard dives into Aquaman
snippet.description:
American actress Amber Heard stars as Princess Mera in AQUAMAN, directed by James Wan, alongside Jason Momoa. A native Texan and fluent in Spanish, Amber sat down with Mariana Medina, in Miami,  to talk about this soaked project, her strong character, and more. AQUAMAN  dives into theaters on December 21st!!! Watch the exclusive interview in Spanish:
